sum buffer cells: buffer of 4 i32 gives i32:
  let total be 0
  let i be 0
  while i is less than 4:
    total becomes total plus cells at i
    i becomes i plus 1
  total

main gives i32:
  let cells be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 0
  cells at 0 becomes 1
  cells at 1 becomes 2
  cells at 2 becomes 3
  cells at 3 becomes 4
  sum buffer cells
